Module lanej.schedulingsystem

Package lanej.schedulingsystem.model

package lanej.schedulingsystem.model
Provides the model classes that represent the core business entities of the scheduling system. They are mapped directly to the tables in an ERD diagram that I was basing the software structure on. These classes define the primary data structures used in the Scheduling application, capturing details about appointments, customers, contacts, users, and related entities.

The model package serves as the backbone for the system, ensuring data consistency and encapsulating the properties and behaviors associated with each entity.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Jonathan Lane
